A group, Plateau PDP Youth Ambassadors for JT Useni 2019 has claimed that Senator Jeremiah Useni is the only solution to the challenges bedevilling Plateau State. The group, in a statement jointly signed by its Chairman, Comrade Joseph Dalas, and Secretary, Comrade Monday Mamot, also said it wanted JT Useni to contest for the governorship of the state because of his leadership qualities. The youths said, “JT Useni is welfare-oriented, a development-conscious, sensitive and responsive, as well as a community-oriented leader.” The group boasted that his age would not be a barrier to good leadership, saying his wealth of experience would work well for further development of the state.